I accidently clicked a minion that was chillin on top of the lantern :(.

When U.R.F was up earlier this year, I was doing the intermediate bots to test it out since it was my first U.R.F ever.

Sometime later, I ended up in the enemies base to nab a kill, but I had extremely low health and Flash was on cool down and all their inhibitor turrets were up, so I couldn't walk around. None of our minions were close enough so that they could tank the turrets for me and the bots were closing in on me.

I was panicking then Thresh threw his Lantern to me. The only thing I thought was ''Thresh! This little ass shield ain't gonna help me!'' it took me 10 seconds to realize that I can click the lantern and I did it just in a nick of time too because I was less than a second away from dying.

I always said I would never forget the Lantern when I first started playing and at that time; I almost did {{item:3070}}
